{"tid":2091756,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"摩根大通停用“黑名單”等術語 避免種族歧視","createTime":"2020-07-03T00:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T01:48:35.000Z","uid":164771,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a05aaa0d161fa9c076d91afedfb7ef69853290","tid":2091756,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T00:15:36.000Z","msg":"據外媒報道，知情人士稱，美國最大銀行摩根大通正從其內部技術材料和代碼中刪除&ldquo;黑名單&rdquo;、&ldquo;白名單&rdquo;、&ldquo;主&rdquo;（master）、&ldquo;從&rdquo;（slave）等術語，試圖解決公司內部的種族主義問題。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士稱，這些術語存在於該行的一些技術政策、標準和控制程序中，以及運行某些流程的編程代碼中。<br />\n<br />\n此前谷歌、推特等科技公司已經宣佈了類似政策，摩根大通似乎是第一個這樣做的金融機構。<br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞商學院編程教授Mattan Griffel説，這種術語長期以來一直存在爭議，很難改變。<br />\n<br />\n他説，在銀行代碼中更改這些術語可能需要花費數百萬美元和幾個月的工作，這對銀行來説不是一筆&ldquo;微不足道的&rdquo;投資。"},{"pid":"f410398392ad5ae85107c948aa2e86f8ebcfd169","tid":2091756,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T00:36:33.000Z","msg":"油鼓全部都係白色<br />\n根本就係白人主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ac26241917cdd920b486c7c7fc7c7c788b33cd","tid":2091756,"uid":261913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T00:37:52.000Z","msg":"Mastercard直頭成間執左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97a2b90569e00ea3f3f4551207e9faa21f9a7f9","tid":2091756,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T00:39:13.000Z","msg":"然後一邊勾結中共迫害香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nblm but 港豬dont matter"},{"pid":"2ae446f746a868ea9117dd6cdc6cc3c5ef905b49","tid":2091756,"uid":238920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T00:40:14.000Z","msg":"一個人可以由blacklist就聯想到黑人就聯想到唔好既野<br />\n呢種先叫歧視<br />\n而唔係用黑色呢個字就係歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353ea4a1